definition:
Someone descended from Lud, a man living at the time of the Patriarchs, first mentioned at Gen.10.22; 
 son of: Shem (H8035); 
 brother of: Asshur (H0804H), Elam (H5867C), Arpachshad (H0775) and Aram (H0758)
Group of lud (לוּד "Lud" H3865)
 § Ludim or Lydians = "to the firebrands: travailings"
 the descendants of Lud the son of Shem
